Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_report...ross_clock_pin(25.10)    timing_report...ross_clock_pin(25.10)

Name
       timing_report_enable_report_clock_timing_across_clock_pin

Syntax
       timing_report_enable_report_clock_timing_across_clock_pin    {true    |
       false}

       Default: false

       Enables fanout tracing across clock pins if any  combinational  arc  is
       present.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

